              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>For more than three decades, JDL Industries has helped aviation and aerospace professionals source the primers and paints they need to keep maintenance operations running and comply with strict OEM and military standards.</p><p>Founded in 1987 by an Eastern Airlines Senior Engineer, Jose Lopez, JDL Industries was built on deep industry experience and a practical understanding of the aviation maintenance environment. From day one, our mission has been to provide high-quality coatings, technical training, and exceptional customer service to airlines, aviation repair facilities, and OEMs—both domestically and internationally.</p><p>Today, that mission remains unchanged.</p>",
